list.name: Kamisato Ayaka
list.title: Frostflake Heron
list.description: Daughter of the Yashiro Commission's Kamisato Clan. Dignified and elegant, aswell as wise and strong.

list.name: Jean
list.title: Dandelion Knight
list.description: The righteous and rigorous Dandelion Knight, and Acting Grand Master ofMondstadt's Knights of Favonius.

list.name: Lisa
list.title: Witch of Purple Rose
list.description: The languid but knowledgeable Librarian of the Knights of Favonius, deemed bySumeru Akademiya to be their most distinguished graduate in the past twocenturies.

list.name: Barbara
list.title: Shining Idol
list.description: Every citizen of Mondstadt adores Barbara. She learned the word "idol" from amagazine.

list.name: Kaeya
list.title: Frostwind Swordsman
list.description: An accomplished swordsman and a strategic thinker in the Knights of Favonius,rumored to hail from beyond Mondstadt.

list.name: Diluc
list.title: Dark Side of Dawn
list.description: The tycoon of a winery empire in Mondstadt, unmatched in every possible way.

list.name: Razor
list.title: Wolf Boy
list.description: A boy who lives among the wolves in Wolvendom of Mondstadt, away from humancivilization. As agile as lightning.

list.name: Amber
list.title: Gliding Champion
list.description: Always energetic and full of life, Amber's the best — albeit only — Outriderof the Knights of Favonius.

list.name: Venti
list.title: Windborne Bard
list.description: One of the many bards of Mondstadt, who freely wanders the city's streets andalleys.

list.name: Xiangling
list.title: Exquisite Delicacy
list.description: A renowned chef from Liyue. She's extremely passionate about cooking andexcels at making her signature hot and spicy dishes.

list.name: Beidou
list.title: Uncrowned Lord of the Ocean
list.description: Captain of her crew, The Crux. She's quite an unbound and forthright woman.

list.name: Xingqiu
list.title: Juvenile Galant
list.description: A young man carrying a longsword who is frequently seen at book booths. He hasa chivalrous heart and yearns for justice and fairness for all.

list.name: Xiao
list.title: Vigilant Yaksha
list.description: A yaksha adeptus who defends Liyue. Also heralded as the "Conqueror of Demons"and "Vigilant Yaksha."

list.name: Ningguang
list.title: Eclipsing Star
list.description: The Tianquan of the Liyue Qixing. Her wealth is unsurpassed in all of Teyvat.

list.name: Klee
list.title: Fleeing Sunlight
list.description: An explosives expert and a regular at the Knights of Favonius's confinementroom. Also known as Fleeing Sunlight.

list.name: Zhongli
list.title: Vago Mundo
list.description: A mysterious expert contracted by the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor. Extremelyknowledgeable in all things.

list.name: Fischl
list.title: Prinzessin der Verurteilung!
list.description: A mysterious girl who calls herself "Prinzessin der Verurteilung" and travelswith a night raven named Oz.

list.name: Bennett
list.title: Trial by Fire
list.description: A good-natured adventurer from Mondstadt who's unfortunately extremelyunlucky.

list.name: Tartaglia
list.title: Childe
list.description: No. 11 of The Harbingers, also known as "Childe." His name is highly feared onthe battlefield.

list.name: Noelle
list.title: Chivalric Blossom
list.description: A maid who faithfully serves the Knights of Favonius. She dreams of joiningtheir ranks someday.

list.name: Qiqi
list.title: Icy Resurrection
list.description: An apprentice and herb gatherer at Bubu Pharmacy. An undead with a bone-whitecomplexion, she seldom has much in the way of words or emotion.

list.name: Chongyun
list.title: Frozen Ardor
list.description: A young exorcist from a family of exorcists. He does everything he can tosuppress his abundance of yang energy.

list.name: Ganyu
list.title: Plenilune Gaze
list.description: The secretary at Yuehai Pavilion. The blood of the qilin, an illuminatedbeast, flows within her veins.

list.name: Albedo
list.title: Kreideprinz
list.description: A genius known as the Kreideprinz, he is the Chief Alchemist and Captain ofthe Investigation Team of the Knights of Favonius.

list.name: Diona
list.title: Kätzlein Cocktail
list.description: A young lady who has inherited trace amounts of non-human blood. She is theincredibly popular bartender of the Cat's Tail tavern.

list.name: Mona
list.title: Astral Reflection
list.description: A mysterious young astrologer who proclaims herself to be "Astrologist MonaMegistus," and who possesses abilities to match the title. Erudite, butprideful.

list.name: Keqing
list.title: Driving Thunder
list.description: The Yuheng of the Liyue Qixing. Keqing has much to say about Rex Lapis'sunilateral approach to policymaking in Liyue — but in truth, gods admireskeptics such as her quite a lot.

list.name: Sucrose
list.title: Harmless Sweetie
list.description: An alchemist filled with curiosity about all things. She researches bio-alchemy.

list.name: Xinyan
list.title: Blazing Riff
list.description: Liyue's sole rock 'n' roll musician. She rebels against ossified prejudicesusing her music and passionate singing.

list.name: Rosaria
list.title: Thorny Benevolence
list.description: A sister of the church, though you wouldn't know it if it weren't for herattire. Known for her sharp, cold words and manner, she often works alone.

list.name: Hu Tao
list.title: Fragrance in Thaw
list.description: The 77th Director of the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor. She took over the businessat a rather young age.

list.name: Kaedehara Kazuha
list.title: Scarlet Leaves Pursue Wild Waves
list.description: A wandering samurai from Inazuma who is currently with Liyue's Crux Fleet. Agentle and carefree soul whose heart hides a great many burdens from the past.

list.name: Yanfei
list.title: Wise Innocence
list.description: A well-known legal adviser active in Liyue Harbor. A brilliant young lady inwhose veins runs the blood of an illuminated beast.

list.name: Yoimiya
list.title: Frolicking Flames
list.description: Owner of Naganohara Fireworks. Known as the "Queen of the Summer Festival,"she excels in her craft of creating fireworks that symbolize people's hopesand dreams.

list.name: Thoma
list.title: Protector From Afar
list.description: The Kamisato Clan's housekeeper. A well-known "fixer" in Inazuma.

list.name: Eula
list.title: Dance of the Shimmering Wave
list.description: The Spindrift Knight, a scion of the old aristocracy, and the Captain of theKnights of Favonius Reconnaissance Company. The reason for which a descendantof the ancient nobles might join the Knights remains a great mystery inMondstadt to this very day.

list.name: Raiden Shogun
list.title: Plane of Euthymia
list.description: Her Excellency, the Almighty Narukami Ogosho, who promised the people ofInazuma an unchanging Eternity.

list.name: Sayu
list.title: Mujina Ninja
list.description: A pint-sized ninja attached to the Shuumatsuban, who always seems sleep-deprived.

list.name: Sangonomiya Kokomi
list.title: Pearl of Wisdom
list.description: The Divine Priestess of Watatsumi Island. All of the island's affairs are atthis young lady's fingertips.

list.name: Gorou
list.title: Canine Warrior
list.description: The great general of Watatsumi Island's forces. He is deeply trusted by hissubordinates.

list.name: Kujou Sara
list.title: Crowfeather Kaburaya
list.description: A general of the Tenryou Commission. Bold, decisive, and skilled in battle.

list.name: Arataki Itto
list.title: Hanamizaka Heroics
list.description: The first and greatest head of the Arataki Gang, famed throughout InazumaCity's Hanamizaka... Wait, what? You've never heard of them? Are you trying tobe funny here?

list.name: Yae Miko
list.title: Astute Amusement
list.description: Lady Guuji of the Grand Narukami Shrine. Also serves as the editor-in-chief ofYae Publishing House. Unimaginable intelligence and cunning are hidden underher beautiful appearance.

list.name: Shikanoin Heizou
list.title: Analytical Harmony
list.description: A young prodigy detective from the Tenryou Commission. His senses are sharpand his thoughts are clear.

list.name: Yelan
list.title: Valley Orchid
list.description: A mysterious person who claims to work for the Ministry of Civil Affairs, butis a "non-entity" on the Ministry of Civil Affairs' list.

list.name: Aloy
list.title: Savior From Another World
list.description: Formerly an outcast, now a hunter of unparalleled skill. Ready to do the rightthing at any time.

list.name: Shenhe
list.title: Lonesome Transcendence
list.description: An adepti disciple with a most unusual air about her. Having spent much timecultivating in isolation in Liyue's mountains, she has become every bit ascool and distant as the adepti themselves.

list.name: Yun Jin
list.title: Stage Lucida
list.description: A renowned Liyue opera singer who is skilled in both playwriting and singing.Her style is one-of-a-kind, exquisite and delicate, much like the personherself.

list.name: Kuki Shinobu
list.title: Mender of Tribulations
list.description: The capable and reliable Arataki Gang deputy leader. Please note: capable andreliable are not appellations for the "Arataki Gang," but for their deputyleader in specific.

list.name: Kamisato Ayato
list.title: Pillar of Fortitude
list.description: The young but highly accomplished head of the Yashiro Commission's KamisatoClan. Cultured and polite, he is a man of many ways and means.

list.name: Collei
list.title: Sprout of Rebirth
list.description: A trainee ranger active in Avidya Forest. Behind her enthusiastic words andactions hides a slightly introverted personality.

list.name: Dori
list.title: Treasure of Dream Garden
list.description: An elusive merchant who has a fondness for glittering Mora.

list.name: Tighnari
list.title: Verdant Strider
list.description: A young researcher well-versed in botany who currently serves as a ForestWatcher in Avidya Forest. He is a straight shooter with a warm heart — and adab hand at guiding even the dullest of pupils.

list.name: Nilou
list.title: Dance of Lotuslight
list.description: The star of the Zubayr Theater. She is full of warmth and innocence, and herdances are lively and elegant.

list.name: Cyno
list.title: Judicator of Secrets
list.description: The General Mahamatra in charge of supervising the researchers of theAkademiya. It is said that when he gets down to work, the General Mahamatra iseven more efficient than the "Great Vayuvyastra" made by the Kshahrewar.

list.name: Candace
list.title: Golden Vow
list.description: A descendant of King Deshret with an amber left eye. The defender of AaruVillage.

list.name: Nahida
list.title: Physic of Purity
list.description: A caged bird secluded within the confines of the Sanctuary of Surasthana whocan only see the world in her dreams.

list.name: Layla
list.title: Fantastical Evening Star
list.description: A Rtawahist student who specializes in Theoretical Astrology. Heavily prone tosomnambulism and locked in a grinding war with sleep deprivation, the problemof restful slumber is a most troubling one to her.

list.name: Wanderer
list.title: Eons Adrift
list.description: A wayfaring figure whose identity is a mystery. He dresses like a mountainascetic, but he certainly does not act the part.

list.name: Faruzan
list.title: Enigmatic Machinist
list.description: A researcher from "one hundred years ago." She enjoys self-identifying aseveryone's senior, and has significant knowledge of ancient scripts andmachines of all kinds.

list.name: Yaoyao
list.title: Burgeoning Grace
list.description: Streetward Rambler's youngest disciple. A gentle and caring "little adult."

list.name: Alhaitham
list.title: Admonishing Instruction
list.description: The current scribe of the Sumeru Akademiya, a man endowed with extraordinaryintelligence and talent. He lives free — free from the searching eyes ofordinary people, anyway.

list.name: Dehya
list.title: Flame-Mane
list.description: A member of the Eremites, a mercenary organization that roams the sands ofSumeru. Valiant and powerful, she enjoys great fame amongst her fellowEremites.

list.name: Mika
list.title: Coordinates of Clear Frost
list.description: A young knight born to an ordinary family. He serves as a Front-Line Surveyorin his Company. He is a low-key and cautious character.

list.name: Kaveh
list.title: Empyrean Reflection
list.description: A renowned architect from Sumeru who perhaps cares a bit too much about toomany things. He is an aesthete troubled by reality.

list.name: Baizhu
list.title: Beyond Mortality
list.description: The owner of Bubu Pharmacy, who is rarely seen without the white snake namedChangsheng. His medicinal knowledge is encyclopedic, and his personalintrigues subtle.
